<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">The world body</COREF> says 0 <COREF ID="9" TYPE="IDENT">North Korea</COREF> will need more food in the year 2001 , because of crop devastation brought * on by drought at planting time and typhoons that *T*-1 severely damaged the fall harvest .
<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">The United Nations</COREF> is also appealing for $ 229 million *U* from international donors *PRO*-1 to help <COREF ID="6" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="VOA20001129.2000.2055.mrg-E1" TYPE="APPOS" SUBTYPE="HEAD">Afghanistan</COREF> , <COREF ID="VOA20001129.2000.2055.mrg-E1" TYPE="APPOS" SUBTYPE="ATTRIB">a country shattered * by years of war and the worst drought in three decades</COREF></COREF> .
